			"content": {
				"number": "1",
				"title": "Förslag till basal medicinsk utredning",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h4>Medicinsk utredning</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through; color: #ff0000;\">Medicinsk</span> A</span>namnes inklusive aktuell <br><span style=\"color: #000000;\">l&auml;kemedelsanv&auml;ndning och andra sjukdomar</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>L&auml;karunders&ouml;kning med neurologstatus</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>Ortostatisk blodtrycksm&auml;tning</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>Mini-mental test (MMT)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\">K</span>locktest</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>EKG</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>Datortomografi hj&auml;rna (fr&aring;gest&auml;llning &ndash; degene&shy;rativa f&ouml;r&auml;ndringar eller vaskul&auml;ra skador)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>Laboratorieutredning (f&ouml;r detaljer, se lokalt v&aring;rdprogram)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"s7_16\" class=\"facts skip\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Social utredning</span></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>Civilst&aring;nd, anh&ouml;riga</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>Yrke, eventuell yrkeslegitimation, utbildning</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span><span class=\"tab\"></span>Intressen, fritidsaktiviteter, livsstil</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"tab\"></span>Ekonomi</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>K&ouml;rkort</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Vapenlicens och vapeninnehav<span class=\"tab\"></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span class=\"tab\"></span>Alkoholvanor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
