			"content": {
				"number": "3",
				"title": "Konfusionssymtom ",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Centrala konfusionssymtom (specifika symtom)</span></h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Bristande uppm&auml;rksamhet och nedsatt <br>koncentrationsf&ouml;rm&aring;ga</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Feltolkningar av sinnesintryck</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Fragmenterat t&auml;nkande</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Psykomotorisk hypo- eller hyperaktivitet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Sekund&auml;ra symtom vid konfusion (icke-specifika symtom)</h4>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Psykisk oro</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Desorientering</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Minnesst&ouml;rning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S&ouml;mn- eller vakenhetsst&ouml;rning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Hallucinationer/illusioner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Paranoida f&ouml;rest&auml;llningar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>Aggressivitet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
