			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"18136\"></a>Läkemedel som visats påverka kognitiva funktioner negativt eller ge upphov till <a class=\"index\" id=\"1034078\" data-text=\"konfusion:behandling\"></a>konfusion (se i övrigt Demenssjukdomar (1))",
				"id": "s7_55",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>L&auml;kemedelsgrupp</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>L&auml;kemedel</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Evidens (styrka)</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Antikolinerga l&auml;kemedel</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Skopolamin</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Bensodiazepiner</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Diazepam</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Antihistaminer</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Difenhydramin, hydroxizin, prometazin</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Glukokortikoider</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Opioider</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Antiepileptika</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Karbamazepin, fenytoin, fenobarbital</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">M&aring;ttligt stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Tricykliska antidepressiva</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Amitriptylin, imipramin, klomipramin</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">M&aring;ttligt stark</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Medel vid Parkinsons sjukdom</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">L-dopa, dopaminagonister, MAO-h&auml;mmare,</div>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">COMT-h&auml;mmare</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Begr&auml;nsad</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Neuroleptika</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Haloperidol</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class=\"tableLine\">Begr&auml;nsad</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
